## ðŸš¨ ERROR RECOVERY
```bash
# Service Recovery
brew services restart postgresql@14
brew services restart redis
pkill -f "node.*3000" && npm run dev

# Clean Slate
rm -rf node_modules package-lock.json
npm install
npm run build
```

